 M. Herman et al [He01, He02]. This code integrates               5634 1451
 into a single system a number of important modules               5634 1451
 and features:                                                    5634 1451
                                                                  5634 1451
 - Spherical and deformed Optical Model including                 5634 1451
   coupled-channels (ECIS03 by J. Raynal)                         5634 1451
